                                Purity tester
                                ~~~~~~~~~~~~~

ý
    This program is not for the easily-offended. When you run the program,
you are given a list of subjects in which you must answer the questions
given using YES or NO. When you have answered all 12 sets of questions,
the computer gives you a purity reading based on the answers you have
given.

    Note that some of the questions asked are EXTREMELY perversed, so this
program is not for children, or the easily-offended.




