                                  Rebound
                                  ~~~~~~~

ý
    This little game is a version of Pong, with a bit better graphics than
the original. The game requires 2 players, and you must get the ball across
to the other players goal area.

    This disk is freely distributable amongst all possible means of media
transfer, as long as no more than one pound is charged.

